file_content.text: The Works remains secure in the orange equilateral.
The power-darkness is obsolete! The conduits are fully functional, and I have witnessed through our monitors.
Also, you destroyed many enemy droid-machines, so well done!
Coruscant's power supply is safe? No more blackouts?
Now. Not eternally. In one millennium, if our interests intersect, we will ask for help again.
Droid, your bizarre praise makes it all worthwhile.
Please remember Gree technology is exclusive to the enclave. Do not attempt to duplicate, or you will be absorbed into the gray pentachoron.
To the Works! Take the tool-sphere repair-mother and repair all conduits.
Are you hoping to speak? Pat-aK should be the object of your attention.
